Ceiling crack repair completed for a homeowner here in Fort Worth.
A drywall seam crack had formed across the living room ceiling between recessed lights, which is a common issue as homes settle over time. We opened the crack, reinforced the seam, applied fresh joint compound, and carefully matched the existing ceiling texture. After blending and painting, the repair now disappears into the rest of the ceiling.
If you have ceiling cracks, drywall damage, or areas that need texture repair, we can help restore it so it looks like it was never there.
