Completed a window trim repair for a homeowner in Fort Worth.
The lower section of the window trim had deteriorated and separated from the frame, leaving exposed wood and a visible gap near the sill. This kind of damage can happen over time from moisture, wear, or normal settling.
We repaired the damaged area, secured the trim back into place, sealed the joint, and restored a clean finished appearance so the window looks solid and well-maintained again.
Small trim issues like this can quickly lead to bigger problems if left unaddressed, so fixing them early helps protect the window and keeps the home looking its best.
